Package: coupleCarrierRisk
Type: Package
Title: Evagene Integration Example - Couple Carrier-Risk Screening
Version: 0.1.0
Description: A minimal Evagene REST API integration that takes two
    23andMe raw genotype files, uploads them to scratch individuals,
    retrieves each partner's population-conditioned carrier-frequency
    table, and prints a combined couple-offspring-risk table for
    autosomal-recessive and X-linked-recessive diseases.  Distributed
    as an example; not a validated clinical tool.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.2.0)
